==Finnish==
===Etymology===
Derivative of the noun ''[[vittu]]''
===Noun===
'''vitutus'''

#(''vulgar'') The status of being deeply annoyed, [[pissed off]], as described in [[vituttaa]]. Some females may like to use the word ''[[kyrvitys]]'' instead.

====Related terms====
*[[vittuilija]]
*[[vittuuntunut]]<!--A person experiencing ''vitutus'-->
*[[vituttaa]]

====Usage notes====
*Some females may like to use the word ''[[kyrvitys]]'' instead.
*Often replaced in common language by ''[[hatutus]]'' which rhymes with vitutus.<!--, and is derived from [[hattu]].-->

